              <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-dim)]">
                AiClientгҖҒAiClientBuilderгҖҒChatRequestBuilderгҖҒжү§иЎҢйҖ»иҫ‘гҖҒзӯ–з•Ҙеј•ж“ҺгҖҒйў„жЈҖгҖҒй”ҷиҜҜеҲҶзұ»гҖҒCallStatsгҖҒCancelHandleгҖ?
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--bg-card)]">
              <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-orange-400 mb-1 font-mono">protocol/</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-dim)]">
                ProtocolLoaderпјҲжң¬ең?URL/GitHubпјүгҖҒJSON Schema йӘҢиҜҒеҷЁгҖҒProtocolManifest
                з»“жһ„гҖҒUnifiedRequest зј–иҜ‘гҖҒй…ҚзҪ®зұ»еһӢгҖ?
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--bg-card)]">
              <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-orange-400 mb-1 font-mono">pipeline/</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-dim)]">
                DecoderпјҲSSEгҖҒJSON
                LinesпјүгҖҒSelectorпјҲJSONPathпјүгҖҒAccumulatorпјҲе·Ҙе…·и°ғз”ЁпјүгҖҒFanOutпјҲеӨҡеҖҷйҖүпјүгҖҒEventMapperпјҲз»ҹдёҖдәӢд»¶пјүгҖҒRetry
                дё?Fallback з®—еӯҗгҖ?
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--bg-card)]">
              <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-orange-400 mb-1 font-mono">transport/</h3>
