                varsпјүгҖҒд»Јзҗ?и¶…ж—¶й…ҚзҪ®гҖҒдёӯй—ҙд»¶ж”ҜжҢҒгҖ?
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--bg-card)]">
              <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-orange-400 mb-1 font-mono">resilience/</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-dim)]">
                зҶ”ж–ӯеҷЁпјҲејҖ/еҚҠејҖ/й—ӯпјүгҖҒд»ӨзүҢжЎ¶йҷҗжөҒгҖҒжңҖеӨ§е№¶еҸ‘дҝЎеҸ·йҮҸиғҢеҺӢгҖ?
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--bg-card)]">
              <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-orange-400 mb-1 font-mono">embeddings/</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-dim)]">
                EmbeddingClientгҖҒEmbeddingClientBuilderгҖҒеҗ‘йҮҸиҝҗз®—пјҲдҪҷејҰзӣёдјјеәҰгҖҒж¬§ж°Ҹи·қзҰ»гҖҒзӮ№з§ҜпјүгҖ?
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--bg-card)]">
              <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-orange-400 mb-1 font-mono">cache/ + batch/</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-dim)]">
                её?TTL зҡ?CacheManagerпјҲMemoryCacheгҖҒNullCacheпјүгҖӮеёҰе№¶еҸ‘жҺ§еҲ¶дёҺеӨҡз§Қзӯ–з•Ҙзҡ„
                BatchCollector дё?BatchExecutorгҖ?
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--bg-card)]">
              <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-orange-400 mb-1 font-mono">
                plugins/ + guardrails/ + structured/
              </h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-dim)]">
                Plugin traitгҖҒPluginRegistryгҖҒHookManagerгҖҒдёӯй—ҙд»¶й“ҫгҖӮеҗ«е…ій”®иҜ?жЁЎејҸиҝҮж»Өдё?PII
                жЈҖжөӢзҡ„жҠӨж ҸгҖ?
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <section class="section-alt">
        <div class="container text-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--text)] mb-4">з”?Rust ејҖе§Ӣжһ„е»?/h2>
